metadata.description:
X BANKRUPT 
I was on my way to visit an old friend that I hadn't seen in years. I walked through dark alleys past old houses. Suddenly a cold wet hand grabbed my shoulder from behind and pulled me around. I recognized an orange-colored skeleton skull as I turned. Pure evil was on the loose that night. -m.c.c
